<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">قال الله تعالى:</span> <span class="c2">(إِنَّ خَيْرَ مَنْ اسْتَأْجَرْتَ الْقَوِيُّ الأَمِينُ)</span> <span class="c2">(القصص/٢٦)</span>.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>